
'''Book: Heart of Dryness.by James G. Workman.''' 

URL = http://www.heartofdryness.com/

In an age of permanent drought, this book explores what we might learn from the Kalahari Bushmen about how to manage water resources. It focuses on [[Peer-to-Peer Water Networks]], see review at http://paulbhartzog.org/2010/06/01/heart-dryness-and-peer-peer-water-networks

Seven part excerpts at http://www.circleofblue.org/waternews/2010/world/heart-of-dryness-reversing-the-politics-of-water-scarcity-from-the-kalahari-to-suburbia/


